claim.claim-text:
5. A method of controlling a refrigeration unit during start up of a logic module, the method comprising: 
setting an initial high set point for the refrigeration unit prior to running the logic module; 
waiting for the refrigeration unit to indicate it has achieved the initial high set point; 
setting a low set point if no errors are present; 
waiting for the refrigeration unit to indicate that it has achieved the low set point; and 
signaling higher-level code that logic module is ready for clocks-on.
